text: Itumbiara crinicornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Ernst Friedrich Germar in 1824. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Itumbiara crinicornis. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1824
title: Itumbiara crinicornis
